data.description: Looking for a few acres out of town, but with convenient access to the city of Missoula? 170 Antrim Way in Florence is conveniently located just outside of Missoula, with mature trees, 2 acres, and a cozy 1440 sq.ft home. The home itself features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, as well as an open living area with a beautiful wood stove. The seller will be leaving plenty of fire wood for the winter as well! If firewood is not your thing, the home is equipped with forced air heating and cooling. Perfect for those cold winter evenings or hot summer nights. Outside there is a detached oversized one car garage with ample room for woodworking, storing Montana toys, or animal equipment. For those beautiful Montana evenings, there is a large back deck for relaxing! Another wonderful feature is the fencing suitable for animals of any size. Call Lyric Johnson at 406-381-2245 or your Real Estate professional for a private tour.
